description.narrative: This activity (Support for enhanced election security) is a component of Ghana Electoral Support Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Other bilateral donor' and a budget of £614,266. This component benefits Ghana, and works in the following sector(s): Elections, Security system management and reform. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-10-2011 and the end date is 30-06-2013.
